trans-unit.source: Specifies the visual state of a track bar slider (also known as a thumb) that is drawn with visual styles.
trans-unit.target: 指定視覺化樣式繪製追蹤列滑桿 （也就是捲動方塊） 的可見狀態。

trans-unit.source: The TrackBarThumbState values correspond to the states of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> objects exposed by the following classes: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical> The TrackBarThumbState values are also used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName> class methods that draw the track bar slider.
trans-unit.target: TrackBarThumbState 值對應至狀態<xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>下列類別所公開的物件:- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical>TrackBarThumbState 值也可用做為引數中<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName>類別繪製追蹤列滑桿的方法。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>
